    "created_at": "2025-03-06T02:13:09Z",
    "updated_at": "2025-03-06T02:13:09Z",
    "body": "I found a better way till the time starship fixes it.\nReplace `eval \"$(starship init zsh)\"`\nwith `eval \"${$(starship init zsh)//Program Files/Program\\ Files/}\"`\n\nThis will replace `Program Files` with `Program\\ Files`, and should work after that.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
